---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Oral Sedation Dentistry Lethbridge | Able Family Dental"
  description="Oral sedation dentistry in Lethbridge at Able Family Dental. A prescription pill taken before your appointment produces deep relaxation while you remain conscious. Dr. Tyler Snow certified."
>

  <!-- ============================================================
       HERO
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[42%] pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
      <img
        src="/images/services/hero-oral-sedation.jpg"
        alt=""
        width="800"
        height="600"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-2/3" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-brand-primary), transparent);"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-wide relative py-16 lg:py-24 lg:max-w-[64%]">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-white mb-5" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="text-white hover:text-white/80 transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <a href="/services/" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors">Services</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <a href="/services/sedation/" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors">Sedation</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <span class="text-white">Oral Sedation</span>
      </nav>
      <p class="eyebrow text-white">Sedation Dentistry</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-5xl)] leading-tight text-white max-w-2xl">
        Oral Sedation
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        A prescription sedative taken before your appointment allows you to arrive relaxed and remain deeply at ease throughout treatment, without the need for an IV or inhalation mask.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       CONTENT
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="section-y bg-[var(--color-surface-cool)]">
    <div class="container-wide">

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-14">
        <p class="eyebrow">How it works</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-4xl)] leading-tight text-[var(--color-brand-primary)]">
          Deep relaxation, start to finish
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
          With oral sedation, Dr. Tyler Snow prescribes a sedative medication that you take at home approximately one hour before your appointment. By the time you arrive at Able Family Dental, you will feel noticeably calm and drowsy. You remain conscious throughout the procedure and can respond to questions, but you will be in a deeply relaxed state, and many patients have little to no memory of the visit afterward.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-14">

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] shadow-md flex flex-col">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shrink-0">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4m6-6h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v4M9 3v18m0 0h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9M9 21H5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2V9m0 0h18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-2">Simple to take</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed flex-1">There are no needles or masks involved. You simply take the prescribed pill before leaving home. The medication begins working gradually so that you feel relaxed well before you sit in the dental chair.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] shadow-md flex flex-col">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shrink-0">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-2">Deeper than nitrous</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed flex-1">Oral sedation produces a more profound state of relaxation than nitrous oxide, making it better suited for patients with moderate to severe anxiety, those with a very sensitive gag reflex, or anyone undergoing a lengthy or complex procedure.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] shadow-md flex flex-col">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shrink-0">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-2">You stay conscious</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed flex-1">Although you will feel heavily sedated, you will remain awake and able to follow simple instructions from Dr. Snow. Your safety is monitored throughout the entire appointment by our trained team.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Detail section -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[var(--color-border-soft)] shadow-md">
        <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-3xl)] text-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-4">What to expect & how to prepare</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Because oral sedation affects your coordination and reaction time for several hours after the appointment, you will need a responsible adult to drive you to and from the office. Plan to rest at home for the remainder of the day.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Dr. Tyler Snow is certified in oral sedation and will review your medical history, current medications, and level of anxiety to select the appropriate medication and dosage for your situation. He will provide you with clear pre-appointment and post-appointment instructions at your consultation.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
          {[
            "Arrange for a trusted adult to drive you to and from your appointment",
            "Follow fasting instructions provided by Dr. Snow",
            "Wear comfortable, loose-fitting clothing",
            "Avoid alcohol and sedating medications in the days leading up to your visit",
            "Plan to rest at home for the remainder of the day after your appointment",
          ].map(item => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[var(--color-brand-accent)]" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Not sure which sedation level is right for you? <a href="/services/sedation/" class="text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] font-semibold hover:text-[var(--color-brand-accent-hover)] transition-colors">Compare all sedation options →</a>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       CTA BAND
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] py-16 text-center overflow-hidden relative">
    <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none" viewBox="0 0 1440 160" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M0 60 C 240 20, 480 100, 720 60 C 960 20, 1200 100, 1440 60 L1440 160 L0 160 Z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.03)"/>
    </svg>
    <div class="relative container-wide">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-[length:var(--text-4xl)] text-white leading-tight">Ready to feel comfortable at the dentist?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-[var(--color-text-on-dark-muted)] text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">Call <a href="tel:+14033277202" class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-[var(--color-brand-accent-soft)] transition-colors">403.327.7202</a> or request an appointment online.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/book/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Book Appointment</a>
        <a href="/refer/" class="btn btn-lg border border-white/30 text-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">Refer Patient</a>>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-lg border border-white/30 text-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
